drivers.name: foo2oak-z1
drivers.comments:
This driver is available in the Ghostscript Printer Application

This is a driver developed for the Kyocera KM-1635/2035 copier.

It is possible that this driver will also work for other Oak Technologies OAKT-based printers, but the author cannot test this.

PPD files (and the Foomatic XML files to generate them) come with the driver, therefore we do not supply PPDs here on the OpenPrinting site.

notes:
The KM-2035 is a copier. Only the print function is supported.

Consumables/Refills: Toner Black (15000 prints) - $70 Imaging Drum (150000 prints) - $160 Part numbers: tk410
